Name: Declaring the fourth week of November annually as The Shangri-Las Week.
Title: Resolution declaring the fourth week of November annually as The Shangri-Las Week in the City of New York, celebrating the 60th anniversary of “Leader of the Pack” in 2024, and recognizing The Shangri-Las’ indelible impact on the music of the 1960s and ever since
BodyName: Committee on Cultural Affairs, Libraries and International Relations

History.Description: This Resolution was Introduced by Council
This Resolution was Referred to Comm by Council to the Committee on Cultural Affairs, Libraries and International Relations
